OL,3,CBuilder's warning month before death
OL,5,FThe daughters of a builder who
OL,6,Frecorded a video message warning
OL,7,Ftradespeople to wear personal
OL,8,Fprotective equipment (PPE) when on
OL,9,Fsite as he was dying at home, have
OL,10,Ftold UTV he was 'the strongest person'
OL,11,Fthey knew.
OL,13,FRaymond Callaghan from Keady in Co
OL,14,FArmagh, had worked on building sites
OL,15,Fsince he was an apprentice at the age
OL,16,Fof 17.
OL,18,FHowever, exposure to cement dust
OL,19,Fthroughout his career led to him being
OL,20,Fdiagnosed with pulmonary fibrosis in
OL,21,F2019.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
