OL,5,FHe wanted to raise awareness to other
OL,6,Fpeople working in the industry about
OL,7,Fthe importance of wearing PPE,
OL,8,Fsomething he said he didn't do enough.
OL,10,FThe condition left the father-of-six
OL,11,Fhousebound in the latter stages of his
OL,12,Flife. He died aged 64 a week before
OL,13,FChristmas in 2024.
OL,15,FA month before he died, Raymond
OL,16,Frecorded a video message in the hope
OL,17,Fit was encourage other builders to
OL,18,Fheed health and safety advice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
