OL,3,CBuilder's warning month before death
OL,5,F"If I was able to, I would should
OL,6,Fevery young brickie or tradesman
OL,7,Fexactly what the dangers of cement
OL,8,Fdust have brought me to, but I can't,"
OL,9,Fhe said in the video.
OL,11,FRaymond needed the assistance of
OL,12,Fbreathing apparatus in order to
OL,13,Fbreathe.
OL,15,FIt was one of the changes he needed to
OL,16,Fadjust to following his diagnosis
OL,17,Fafter having to leave the career he
OL,18,Floved. It was also a time of
OL,19,Fadjustment for his family, including
OL,20,Ftwo of his daughters, Maggie and Maeve.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
