OL,3,CBuilder's warning month before death
OL,5,F"Even when he came home he was talking
OL,6,Fabout work, he was telling us stories
OL,7,Fabout work," said Maggie.
OL,9,FShe added: "Even at his wake, people
OL,10,Fwere coming in to tell us about what
OL,11,Fhe had done at work and how he helped
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FMaeve told UTV that the fact her
OL,15,Ffather wanted to help others even when
OL,16,Fit was too late for him was 'a true
OL,17,Ftestament' to his character.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
