OL,3,CBuilder's warning month before death
OL,5,FBand of Builders, a charity which
OL,6,Fhelps families going through difficult
OL,7,Fperiods, was preparing to install a
OL,8,Fnew wet room and extension to the
OL,9,FCallaghan family home in Keady - but
OL,10,FRaymond didn't live long enough to
OL,11,Fwitness the project being completed.
OL,13,FMarcus McGee from the charity said
OL,14,Fnews of his death was 'devastating'.
OL,16,FDespite losing their father, Maggie
OL,17,Fand Maeve say they are happy that he
OL,18,Fgets to leave a legacy of helping
OL,19,Fothers.
